<div tiddler="SaveChanges" modifier="JeremyRuston" modified="200611081026" created="200611081026" tags="" changecount="1">Socialtext Unplugged lets you browse and edit your content while you're offline. When you make a change you need to SaveChanges to save the change to your local hard drive, before later performing a SyncChanges to synchronise the change back to the server.\n\nThe procedure for SaveChanges is slightly different for different browsers:\n* SavingOnInternetExplorer\n* SavingOnFireFox\n* SavingOnSafari\n* SavingOnOpera\n</div>